PortSystem          1.0
PortGroup           golang 1.0

go.setup            github.com/cyberark/summon 0.9.5 v
categories          devel
maintainers         {@0x1DA117 danieltrautmann.com:me} openmaintainer
license             MIT

description         CLI that provides on-demand secrets access for common \
                    DevOps tools.

long_description    summon is a command-line tool to make working with secrets \
                    easier. \
                    It provides an interface for reading a secrets.yml file, \
                    fetching secrets from a trusted store and exporting secret \
                    values to a sub-process environment. \

build.args          -o ${worksrcpath}/${name} ./cmd
build.env-append    CGO_ENABLED=0

destroot {
    xinstall -m 0755 ${worksrcpath}/${name} ${destroot}${prefix}/bin/
}

